properties.name: Sonnberg
properties.note: Rocky promontory, subject to erosion. Middle Triassic shallow marine limestone, Jena Formation (U.-Muschelkalk, Wellenkalk). Small outcrop within E-W trending graben structure. Contact to MIttlerer Buntsandstein exposed in river bed southwest of crag.
